001package com.pingidentity.sdk.pingonewallet.types.WalletEvents;
002
003import com.pingidentity.did.sdk.client.service.model.Challenge;
004import com.pingidentity.sdk.pingonewallet.types.WalletMessage.UnknownMessage;
005
006public class UnknownEvent implements WalletEvent {
007
008    public static WalletEventType TYPE = WalletEventType.UNKNOWN;
009
010    public String applicationInstanceId;
011    public String sender;
012    public Challenge challenge;
013
014    private UnknownMessage unknownMessage;
015
016    public UnknownEvent(String applicationInstanceId, String sender, Challenge challenge, UnknownMessage unknownMessage) {
017        this.applicationInstanceId = applicationInstanceId;
018        this.sender = sender;
019        this.challenge = challenge;
020        this.unknownMessage = unknownMessage;
021    }
022
023    @Override
024    public WalletEventType getType() {
025        return TYPE;
026    }
027
028    @Override
029    public String getSender() {
030        return sender;
031    }
032
033    @Override
034    public Challenge getChallenge() {
035        return challenge;
036    }
037
038    public String getMessage() {
039        return unknownMessage.getRawMessage();
040    }
041
042    public String getApplicationInstanceId() {
043        return applicationInstanceId;
044    }
045}
